<https://danielagarciachavero.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/MDRS-Onto.owl> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> "The medical device ontology is designed to structure and represent information about medical devices and post-market surveillance within the European regulatory framework (MDR/IVDR)."@en .
<https://danielagarciachavero.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/MDRS-Onto.owl> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> "Medical Device Regulatory and Surveillance Ontology"@en .
<https://danielagarciachavero.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/MDRS-Onto.owl> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "Ontology detailing medical devices, post-market surveillance, incidents, and field safety corrective actions compliant with EU MDR/IVDR regulations."@en .
